.if t .2C
.nh 1 "The Dependency Maintenance Tool"
.LP
Aegis places heavy demands on the dependency maintenance tool,
so it is important that you select an appropriate one.
This chapter talks about what a dependency tool requires,
and gives examples of how to use the various alternatives.
.LP
At this writing,
the author has seen few sufficiently capable dependency maintenance tools.
